  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable&nbsp;</strong><strong>oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>beef mince,&nbsp;baharat,</strong>&nbsp;a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cook for 3-4 min, breaking it up as you go</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, lay the <strong>tortillas</strong> onto baking trays, making sure they don't overlap&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Divide the <strong>tahini</strong>&nbsp;<strong>paste</strong> between the <strong>tortillas</strong> and spread it out, just as you would buttering bread</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>cooked</strong><strong>&nbsp;beef mince</strong>&nbsp;equally between the <strong>tortillas</strong></p>\r\n<p>Put them in the oven for 10-12 min or until they're crispy and browned - these are your <strong>Turkish flatbreads</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tip: keep an eye on them, you want them crispy but not burnt!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice the <strong>spring onion</strong><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p>\r\n<p>Crumble the<strong> feta</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel lengths off the<strong> courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span>&nbsp;</strong>until you end up with a pile of<strong> courgette&nbsp;'ribbons'</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787_s-tep-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of both&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>&nbsp;to a large bowl</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>crumbled feta</strong>,<strong> sliced spring onion</strong> and<strong> courgette ribbons&nbsp;</strong>and give everything a good mix up<strong> &nbsp;</strong>- this is your <strong>courgette&nbsp;salad</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
