          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/787.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong> into a small mixing bowl</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>mayonnaise</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;and give everything a good mix - this is your <strong>aioli</strong></p>\r\n<p>Pick the<strong> parsley leaves </strong>from the stalks, discarding the stalks&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
